Package: TidySoils
Type: Package
Title: Tidy Tools for Soil Science
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Einar", "Taakefyrsten", , "einaremil1999@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-5872-4959"))
Description: A meta-package that installs and attaches the TidySoils
    ecosystem: tidysoiltexture for USDA texture classification and
    ggplot2-based texture triangle plots, and tidysoilwater for Van
    Genuchten soil water retention and unsaturated hydraulic conductivity
    modelling. All packages are pipe-compatible, accept and return tibbles,
    and use tidy evaluation for column arguments.
